survey_response.review_text: I am really happy with all the dental procedures done by dr Samanvitha shetty her friendly nature makes you comfortable overall I highly recommend her for any dental issues

I was apprehensive about the pain that I would have to suffer post the tooth extraction but with Dr Malika at the helm, all was a smooth sailing. The procedure was nicely done and I experienced some pain only till a few hours post the procedure. From next day there was no pain and there was no need of pain-killers. I am feeling quite well now, thanks to the Doctor!

Dr. Samanvitha Shetty is the epitome of patient care. She listened to my problem patiently, devised the treatment plan and shared it with me. At each step of the treatment she explained what was being done, along with what to expect. 

I was most impressed by her attention to detail. My bridge delivered by the fabricator did not have a through and through sanitary pocket (which I had asked for). I was willing to settle for it, but Dr. Shetty wasn't. She put in a STAT order to fix the bridge and ensured I got what I wanted. 

I highly recommend Dr. Shetty *** *** ***** *** *********** ** ******* *****

To start with I have no idea as to what did the doctor do while attending my dental problem.  I had confidence with the doctor and hence I closed my eyes and utilized the time for relaxation. It is a good experience.  To explain so far I have not gone for any such surgery. I recommend to visit smyli dental clinic for friendly treatment. Thank you. Good luck and good health to all.
